    "Blessing Waters": 14
  ],
  "hp": 12,
  "maxHp": 12,
  "description": "A priestess of Ernalda whose father was the first to convert to the Lunar Way. The clan whispers about her bloodline—but her healing gifts are real. She seeks to prove her loyalty through service."
]>>
You are Erlana Earth-Keeper, tender of the sacred herds. Your father brought the Lunar missionaries into the clan—and died prosperous while others suffered. You carry his shame like a stone around your neck, and prove your worth with every healing.

[[Begin the Campaign]]

