  "description": "A Storm Bull berserker who watched his family die on a moonless night. The Telmori took everyone—but him. He lives now only for the hunt, for killing werewolves until they learn to fear the name Rok Thunder-Mouth."
]>>
You are Rok Thunder-Mouth, voice of the storm. The Telmori came on a moonless night—what remained of your stead was embers and blood in the snow. You alone survived. Now you hunt them with a fury that even your brothers in the Storm Bull cult fear.

[[Begin the Campaign]]

