]>>
You are Asvith Silver-Step, rider of the border. You serve Jomes, the Lunars' puppet—but you feed information to the rebels. Somewhere in this clan sits the man who sold your father to the wolves. You wait. You watch. You ride.

[[Begin the Campaign]]

